\begin_layout Standard
In principle, given limitless data, we could separately apply eqn
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:SP"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

