 However, the principle does illustrate the great power of 
\emph on
known-age
\emph default
 mark-recapture data.
 Note also that there are no assumptions about equiprobable sampling across
 ages, etc; all probabilities are simply conditioned on observed ages, and
 it does not particularly matter 
\emph on
why
\emph default
